{"type": "article", "id": 23599, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 24682, "name": "Kibardin Design"}, {"id": 15321, "name": "Sovrappensiero"}, {"id": 24683, "name": "Kate & Kate"}, {"id": 24684, "name": "Petr Kudlacek"}, {"id": 24685, "name": "Marcel Sigel"}, {"id": 24686, "name": "Michael Samoriz"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112454cEs5geB3pUaLzt7u.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>Melancholia by Kibardin Design</h2>\n<p>这款挂钟完全模糊了指针和刻度的概念。它由前后两个颜色不同的圆盘组成，都只带有一个很小的缺口，分别指示小时和分钟，极简但巧妙。如果不是特别注意，会忘记这是一个钟，它缓解了因时间带来的紧张感。设计者来自俄罗斯，他们设计了很多极简的时钟，这款钟有 6 种颜色，<a href=\"http://www.kibardindesign.com/products/collection/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105537bYQDGje5RL9Sx1Ky.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105538deufjl3PNVM6rcty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105538fpQ7wB6kVCvWXbGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105538QaMG9yEiqfDNTern.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105539lAp8ROBwV3WE7FnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>“furnature”by sovrappensiero</h2>\n<p>这是米兰设计工作室 sovrappensiero 的实验项目，他们想将作品设计成“不完整”的样子。比如桌子的腿并不能维持平衡，需要放上一块石头来维持重力，晾衣架也是如此。另一些物品需要加入配合的物品才有实际的功能，比如花瓶和花，毛巾架和毛巾。它提醒了人们产品和使用者之间的关系，<a href=\"http://www.sovrappensiero.com/work/furnature/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105539poaZKNJSvfdqPBXs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105540hWgTnB6iPje9HO0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77261614\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105540bpQqES7ZW1htNJ4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105540sgn8pN9KtfLwjbDG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105541e9ILkOHuM1BGCJoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22127139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105541780uqR2pmDXekbtx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46332518\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“lunar”by Marcel Sigel &amp; gohome</h2>\n<p>这组椅子来自澳大利亚设计师 Marcel Sigel ，一共有三款。相同点在于它的弧形座位面，让椅子多了一个转折，有了深浅光影的变化。突出的弧形结构正好在腰的位置，也很舒适。椅腿有交叉橡木腿、金属和带轮子三种，可以适应居家办公等多个环境。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055421K0HT8ja4gRDfykO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105542E4ip60ADBCFWZ2TR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03178484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055432sn7uAt8C5brR9ih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105543ty3qarPzSmlUnZf9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.02322738\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105543Sg8nNvsObikL3TQf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Exhale by Kate &amp; Kate </h2>\n<p>这是澳大利亚做纺织设计的品牌 Kate &amp; Kate 推出的 2016 冬季系列，包括毯子、垫子、枕套等棉纺织品。他们擅长用不同颜色的色块做出拼接效果，比如方形的色块大小深浅错落排列，很有艺术感。也有方格、条纹等普通的样式，但色调偏灰，偶尔使用粉色或蓝色提亮，给人柔和舒适的感受。售价 119 美元起，<a href=\"http://kateandkate.com.au/shop/category/new/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105544r4UltAJWyGZC5YiT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105544zh7EC58H2wFPcL6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105545zDS0ubp8x49mQ76H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055456GbPKXSjsAI2fe54.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105546yizP97l4BugorkFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Helix lamp by Michael Samoriz</h2>\n<p>这盏灯就像一个放大的钨丝圈，来自乌克兰的年轻设计师 Michael Samoriz。实际上灯泡的一段在最下面，上面大部分都是灯管，从侧面看就是一个渐渐缩小的圆环，体现出极简现代的特征。悬挂这盏灯的线很长，让它可以适合餐厅、酒吧等环境。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055465uMZWDSrEcOzLRAB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105546c51XCKaOQguhMFd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105547X8EHNCnVIsSta9JZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055470CE6QD74KbksSfxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105547ZISKpDz8AOoMcn7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<h2>FLASHTONES by Petr Kudlacek</h2>\n<p>捷克袜子品牌 FLASHTONES 的特色就是彩色的袜子，设计师在设计包装时想到了抽纸。他们利用回收后的硬纸板制作了方形盒子，正上方的大圆露出了袜子的颜色，也有衬托和表现颜色的作用。每只袜子装进一个小盒子里，鼓励随意搭配，穿不一样的袜子，这种活泼的做法正好配合了活泼的颜色。纸板上有金色的字母以标注品牌。<a href=\"http://www.flashtones.cz\">这里是品牌链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105548Ha9L6zo5K4M2bBXt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105548cwq5bXhuLV2mY8B6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105549FuStrVYW62f1Ekha.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055490tvH96CLMld7mX3u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071055494p0jzSK3txDm67yd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}